  <pre class="pCode2" >
</pre>    
<p class="pCodeShiftBottom"></p>
<a name="wp3687300"> </a><p class="pBody" >
Ensures that the programmable counter&#8217;s <code class="cCodeBody">count</code> variable only decrements by 1. If <code class="cCodeBody">count</code> wraps, the assertion fails, because the change is not a binary decrement.  </p>    <div align="left"><img src="images/ovl_checkers44.gif" height="77" width="459" border="0" vspace="0" hspace="100" />  </div>	
